Key Match Events: Travis Head scored 137 runs off 120 balls
Rohit Sharma was dismissed by Travis Head for 66 runs
Australia won the match by 6 wickets with 42 balls remaining
Post-Match Reflections: Travis Head's performance was praised as mature across all formats by Tom Moody
Australia won their sixth World Cup title
Miscellaneous Highlights: Travis Head took a spectacular catch to dismiss Rohit Sharma
Pat Cummins' decision to bowl first was a key factor in the match
Others: The match was played in Ahmedabad, India
The match was the final of the ICC Cricket World Cup 2023-24
